parameters.query:
select sb.RutDv, sb.RazonSocial ,null as Ranking, 0 as GranPagador, 
CASE
	WHEN sb.RubroEconomico = "CONSTRUCCION" THEN 1     
	WHEN sb.RubroEconomico = "ACTIVIDADES INMOBILIARIAS" THEN 1     ELSE 0 END as Blocked, 0 as PagadorProntoPago, now() as createdAt , 
CASE     
	WHEN sb.RUT  BETWEEN 60000000 and 61999999 THEN "A+"     
	WHEN sb.RubroEconomico = "CONSTRUCCION" THEN "C"     
	WHEN sb.RubroEconomico = "ACTIVIDADES INMOBILIARIAS" THEN "C"     	
	WHEN sb.TramoSegunVentas BETWEEN 12 and 13 then "A+"     
	WHEN sb.TramoSegunVentas BETWEEN 10 and 11 then "A"     
	WHEN sb.TramoSegunVentas BETWEEN 8 and 9 then "B+"     
	WHEN sb.TramoSegunVentas BETWEEN 5 and 7 then "B"     ELSE "C" END    as newRanking
from SII_BUSINESS sb
left join CUMPLO_PAYERS cp on cp.RutDv = sb.RutDv  
where cp.RUT is null and  sb.RUT is not null  and sb.RutDv = '763489663'
order by 1 asc;
SELECT UPPER(RutDv) as RutDv,RazonSocial FROM CUMPLO_PAYERS;
